==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: In life, where will you not run into other people.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: rén shēng hé chù bù xīang féng

===Phrase===
'''[[人生]][[何]][[处]][[不]][[相逢]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') Even if you are separated from somebody by great distances, there is always a chance that you may bump into him someday.

===Alternate forms===
[[人生]][[何]][[處]][[不]][[相逢]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

